the most transparent,

129
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:12,510
yet whose stories are the most opaque.

130
00:04:12,510 --> 00:04:14,640
Today, you only have one mission.

131
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:16,870
It is to shoot the cover of a magazine

132
00:04:16,870 --> 00:04:20,670
