133
00:04:20,670 --> 00:04:21,850
This way please.

134
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:31,720
The set is ready.

135
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,480
You may all come down.

136
00:04:36,860 --> 00:04:40,020
(An Ke, the fifth son)

137
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:42,400
This is Mr. Ke.

138
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:44,200
The youngest son of our founder,

139
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:46,520
(Butler Mr. Wu; Photographer; Cleaner Pai)
An Songqiu.

140
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:48,480
That makes him the youngest uncle.

141
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:51,000
I've worked in this household
for 20 years

142
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,320
and have never seen him

143
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:53,640
make a mistake.

144
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,160
Don't worry.

145
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:56,960
You have me.

146
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:58,240
So he's the legendary

147
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,240
dreamy uncle.

148
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:01,600
Mr. Ke,

149
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,880
the items you requested are all here.

150
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,240
Mr. Ning.

151
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:13,480
He is

152
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,920
(An Xiaoning, the eldest grandson)
the eldest son

153
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,600
of the chairman and his late wife.

154
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:18,960
The eldest grandson
of the An family, An Xiaoning.

155
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:20,880
Mr. Ning,

156
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:24,000
your wife has returned
to the country with your child.

157
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:24,640
What?

158
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:26,760
She's back?

159
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:27,880
Yes.

160
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:29,720
Here.

161
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,640
Hand this to her.

162
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,840
As long as she carries my bead,

163
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:36,200
no one will touch her

164
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:37,720
in the detective circle.

165
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,080
Yes.

166
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:41,640
Ning.

167
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:43,880
Uncle Ke.

168
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:46,600
How are you?

169
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:47,880
Not too bad.

170
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,800
As the largest glass family,

171
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:52,920
I specially made a glass bracelet

172
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:53,840
for you.

173
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,360
I hope you like it.

174
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,400
Alright, Uncle Ke.

175
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:57,200
Thank you.

176
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,160
Quite solid.

177
00:06:07,100 --> 00:06:09,020
(An Xiaowen, the granddaughter)

178
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,160
This is

179
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:12,480
the only daughter of the An family,

180
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,320
An Xiaowen.

181
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:17,000
She is the daughter of the chairman

182
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:20,280
and his late wife.

183
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:22,080
The whole scene feels different now.

184
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:25,920
It hurts.

185
00:06:28,540 --> 00:06:31,700
(He Jiahuan,
son-in-law of the An family)

186
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:34,520
Darling, why didn't you wait for me?

187
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:35,560
That's her husband.

188
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:38,240
Heir to Wang Tech,

189
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,360
He Jiahuan.

190
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,680
Why is it swollen?

191
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,360
Who hurt you?

192
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:44,960
It itches.

193
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:46,080
Then take a shower.

194
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:48,200
Mr. Wu!

195
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,440
Yes, sir.

196
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:51,320
Pull all surveillance footage

197
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,520
in the area right this instant!

198
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,320
I want to know

199
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,880
which mosquito

200
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:55,960
hurt my wife.

201
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:59,160
But it already flew away.

202
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:02,520
Then find out

203
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:03,600
where it came rom.

204
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:05,160
Was it the bushes at the gate?

205
00:07:07,440 --> 00:07:08,480
It's getting cold.

206
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:11,080
Time to let that landscape company

207
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:11,840
go bankrupt.

208
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:14,040
Every bump on your face

209
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:15,960
means one mosquito

210
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:17,960
must die in this world.

211
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:21,880
I've long disliked He Jiahua.

212
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:24,440
Let's beat him up later.

213
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:25,440
Me too.

214
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:26,560
He's too handsome.

215
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:28,840
Tmall 618 Festival.

216
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,200
Continue.

217
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:34,200
Tmall 618 Festival.
Big discounts on selected items.

218
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,280
Tmall is the best.

219
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:36,720
I'll clear your cart

220
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,800
