253
00:08:43,550 --> 00:08:45,000
(Jin Xiangyu, the matriarch)
The current An family madam,

254
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:45,920
Jin Xiangyu,

255
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:48,960
and her son who is the youngest grandson
of the An family,

256
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,040
Coming, Mom.

257
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:50,560
An Xiaoding.

258
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:55,840
What I love most

259
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:58,160
is sugar-free cola from Italy

260
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:02,080
and my son who shines like crystal.

261
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:02,600
Here.

262
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,120
Quick!

263
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:03,720
Hurry!

264
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,320
Come on.

265
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:06,760
She moves quick like a descending fairy.

266
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:08,480
So fast.

267
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:09,880
Alright.

268
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:10,760
Everyone's here.

269
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,680
Yes.

270
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:12,680
I also prepared gifts for you two.

271
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:13,960
Uncle Ke got gifts for you two.

272
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,040
A shattered butterfly.

273
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,800
