686
00:21:51,520 --> 00:21:52,080
Yes.

687
00:21:52,180 --> 00:21:52,980
(Current case summary. Victim: An Er.
Location: An family second-floor hall)

688
00:21:52,980 --> 00:21:54,220
(Time of death:
March 24, 2016 10:03:25AM)

689
00:21:54,220 --> 00:21:55,340
(Cause of death: Poisoned needle wound)

690
