727
00:23:19,480 --> 00:23:20,200
Ding.

728
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:21,720
You too.

729
00:23:22,600 --> 00:23:23,400
Oh, me too.

730
00:23:23,580 --> 00:23:26,060
