781
00:25:09,080 --> 00:25:10,400
You're smart.

782
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:11,520
See?

783
00:25:11,520 --> 00:25:11,840
Yeah.

784
00:25:12,120 --> 00:25:13,040
That's the spot.

785
00:25:13,100 --> 00:25:18,700
