reflection, poison needle launcher)

786
00:25:19,700 --> 00:25:20,460
(Shocked)

787
00:25:20,480 --> 00:25:21,920
Yes.

788
00:25:21,920 --> 00:25:23,760
Unreal.

789
00:25:24,880 --> 00:25:25,880
