841
00:27:00,920 --> 00:27:01,840
You do?

842
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:04,240
Where were you at 10:05 a.m.,

843
00:27:04,240 --> 00:27:04,880
Aunt Pai?

844
00:27:06,380 --> 00:27:09,500
