1147
00:35:32,760 --> 00:35:33,600
I'll use the Restore Card.

1148
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:34,720
(Restore Card: restores one clue)

1149
00:35:34,720 --> 00:35:35,120
Okay.

1150
00:35:35,600 --> 00:35:36,240
Then

1151
00:35:37,000 --> 00:35:38,600
I'll use

1152
00:35:39,680 --> 00:35:41,840
the Restore Card.

1153
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:43,720
(Restore Card)
Player used a Restore Card

1154
00:35:43,720 --> 00:35:45,600
to restore one clue.

1155
00:35:48,760 --> 00:35:50,000
It actually worked.

1156
00:35:50,260 --> 00:35:52,140
