1157
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:55,400
It's back.

1158
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:56,120
It worked.

1159
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:01,240
It really worked.

1160
00:36:02,520 --> 00:36:05,040
DNA test report.

1161
00:36:05,040 --> 00:36:05,800
What?

1162
00:36:08,720 --> 00:36:09,920
A DNA test?

1163
00:36:10,460 --> 00:36:12,260
(The shredded file was a DNA test report)

1164
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:12,960
Come on.

1165
00:36:12,960 --> 00:36:13,640
Here we go.

1166
00:36:13,640 --> 00:36:15,440
(DNA test report)
Dear Mr. An Er,

1167
00:36:15,440 --> 00:36:16,680
based on your samples,

1168
00:36:16,680 --> 00:36:18,440
DNA analysis confirms

1169
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:19,280
