1170
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:21,680
An Yi and An Xiaoding

1171
00:36:21,680 --> 00:36:24,980
(are not biological father and son.)

1172
00:36:26,940 --> 00:36:29,380
(Shocking reveal)

1173
00:36:29,400 --> 00:36:30,680
He's not my father?

1174
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:32,160
What?

1175
00:36:32,160 --> 00:36:32,600
No.

1176
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:33,520
Mom!

1177
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:35,760
Mom.

1178
00:36:37,360 --> 00:36:38,800
Who's my father?

1179
00:36:40,680 --> 00:36:41,120
Mom.

1180
00:36:41,720 --> 00:36:42,850
Jin Xiangyu.

1181
00:36:42,960 --> 00:36:43,760
Unbelievable!

1182
00:36:44,600 --> 00:36:46,000
Jin Xiangyu.

1183
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:49,240
Who was it?

1184
00:36:49,880 --> 00:36:51,000
Who's his father?

1185
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:52,240
Now you know

1186
00:36:52,240 --> 00:36:54,560
