1187
00:36:54,560 --> 00:36:55,480
I get it.

1188
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:57,480
As for the gift,

1189
00:36:57,480 --> 00:36:58,920
you two

1190
00:36:58,920 --> 00:37:00,360
