1191
00:37:01,360 --> 00:37:02,640
A broken butterfly.

1192
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:04,760
Broken family?

1193
00:37:05,160 --> 00:37:06,160
So, who's your dad?

1194
00:37:06,640 --> 00:37:07,480
(Still rich in Henan)
No wonder.

1195
00:37:07,480 --> 00:37:08,640
Isn't he your dad?

1196
00:37:08,980 --> 00:37:10,340
(For real?)

1197
00:37:10,420 --> 00:37:11,740
