Not me.

1200
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:14,920
No.

1201
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:15,600
No, not me.

1202
00:37:15,600 --> 00:37:16,600
Could you be...

1203
00:37:19,240 --> 00:37:20,000
That's possible.

1204
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:20,920
Maybe Uncle Ke

1205
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:21,740
