1206
00:37:21,740 --> 00:37:23,940
(Explain yourself)

1207
00:37:23,940 --> 00:37:25,320
(No)

1208
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:25,800
I asked

1209
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:26,840
