1212
00:37:28,440 --> 00:37:29,060
(Uncle Ke from Shanxi)

1213
00:37:29,060 --> 00:37:30,660
(Cold sweat)

1214
00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:37,120
An Er kept digging through your clothes.

1215
00:37:38,520 --> 00:37:39,880
So that's why Uncle Er

1216
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:40,920
