1217
00:37:42,160 --> 00:37:44,520
He was digging through my clothes

1218
00:37:44,520 --> 00:37:45,440
for hair.

1219
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:48,920
He wanted your DNA.

1220
00:37:49,160 --> 00:37:50,880
To beat me...

1221
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:52,640
To take power,

1222
00:37:52,640 --> 00:37:54,000
An Er wanted to prove you...

1223
00:37:54,000 --> 00:37:55,240
To prove I had a scandal.

1224
00:37:55,680 --> 00:37:56,200
Exactly.

1225
00:37:56,200 --> 00:37:56,940
(An Er used Jin Xiangyu's
scandal for power)

1226
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:59,200
Jin Xiangyu, explain yourself.

1227
00:37:59,600 --> 00:38:01,360
Show some respect

1228
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:03,240
when talking to your elders,

1229
00:38:03,240 --> 00:38:05,240
even if I'm morally flawed.

1230
00:38:06,600 --> 00:38:09,360
Even if you're morally flawed?

1231
00:38:09,680 --> 00:38:12,320
You're a suspect now.

1232
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:12,760
What right

1233
00:38:12,760 --> 00:38:13,760
do you have

1234
00:38:13,760 --> 00:38:15,640
to act high and mighty here?

1235
00:38:17,200 --> 00:38:21,040
Look how far you've fallen.

1236
00:38:21,640 --> 00:38:22,680
Honestly,

1237
00:38:23,160 --> 00:38:24,720
after I married An Yi,

1238
00:38:24,720 --> 00:38:26,640
