1239
00:38:26,640 --> 00:38:28,680
But before that...

1240
00:38:28,700 --> 00:38:29,480
(I'm not even an An)

1241
00:38:29,480 --> 00:38:29,960
Mom.

1242
00:38:31,080 --> 00:38:33,280
I had one drunken mistake.

1243
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:33,920
With who?

1244
00:38:36,640 --> 00:38:37,040
Mom.

1245
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:39,760
I don't know who he was.

1246
00:38:40,220 --> 00:38:42,020
(So, who is my dad?)

1247
00:38:43,800 --> 00:38:44,640
What?

1248
00:38:45,240 --> 00:38:46,440
How could you?

1249
00:38:46,920 --> 00:38:47,880
How could you?

1250
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:49,680
You don't even know his father?

1251
00:38:49,680 --> 00:38:50,160
You...

1252
00:38:50,480 --> 00:38:51,520
I was drunk.

1253
00:38:52,020 --> 00:38:54,380
(Drunk, and I got hurt)

1254
00:38:54,840 --> 00:38:56,440
Then who tore it up?

1255
00:38:56,880 --> 00:38:57,640
I did.

1256
00:39:01,640 --> 00:39:02,960
One day,

1257
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:04,160
I went over

1258
00:39:04,160 --> 00:39:04,840
and saw it

1259
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:05,800
by the door.

1260
00:39:08,640 --> 00:39:10,160
After I saw the letter...

1261
00:39:10,840 --> 00:39:11,160
Kid...

1262
00:39:11,160 --> 00:39:11,600
Then I...

1263
00:39:11,620 --> 00:39:12,760
(Uncle Ke feels bad for you)

1264
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:13,560
I knew

1265
00:39:14,120 --> 00:39:15,480
I wasn't my mom's...

1266
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:15,760
Wait, no.

1267
00:39:16,120 --> 00:39:17,200
I wasn't my dad's

1268
00:39:17,200 --> 00:39:18,760
real son.

1269
00:39:18,760 --> 00:39:19,600
That's bad.

1270
00:39:19,600 --> 00:39:21,600
I won't have money
to buy haute couture anymore.

1271
00:39:23,100 --> 00:39:24,500
(An Xiaoding always flaunts fashion)

1272
00:39:24,540 --> 00:39:25,380
(DNA Test Report)

1273
00:39:25,880 --> 00:39:26,920
I have a question.

1274
00:39:26,920 --> 00:39:27,880
You said

1275
00:39:27,880 --> 00:39:29,600
(Found a loophole)
you knew about this letter, right?

1276
00:39:29,600 --> 00:39:31,320
When I got to the door, I saw this letter.

1277
00:39:31,320 --> 00:39:31,920
You saw it?

1278
00:39:31,920 --> 00:39:32,920
So you knew it.

1279
00:39:32,920 --> 00:39:34,320
You've always been protecting me.

1280
00:39:34,600 --> 00:39:35,920
But someone knows your secret.

1281
00:39:35,980 --> 00:39:37,320
(This is the key point)

1282
00:39:37,320 --> 00:39:38,200
Yes. I was afraid

1283
00:39:38,680 --> 00:39:39,360
Uncle Er would find out.

1284
00:39:39,840 --> 00:39:41,600
(An Er still doesn't know?)
So, you and your mom

1285
00:39:41,600 --> 00:39:42,880
