1286
00:39:44,480 --> 00:39:44,960
No.

1287
00:39:45,480 --> 00:39:47,400
I just tore this up.

1288
00:39:47,400 --> 00:39:47,720
This letter

1289
00:39:48,040 --> 00:39:49,560
was right outside his door.

1290
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:51,080
He hadn't had time to take it yet.

1291
00:39:51,080 --> 00:39:52,000
You tore this up?

1292
00:39:54,520 --> 00:39:56,040
Because of one tiny action of yours,

1293
00:39:56,040 --> 00:39:57,480
