1294
00:39:57,480 --> 00:39:58,520
You already knew the contents.

1295
00:39:58,520 --> 00:39:59,200
Why didn't you say it?

1296
00:40:00,560 --> 00:40:02,960
Just like that, my Restore Card is gone!

1297
00:40:02,960 --> 00:40:03,640
(You owe me one)

1298
00:40:03,640 --> 00:40:05,200
Don't worry. He still has a Copy Card.

1299
00:40:05,200 --> 00:40:06,280
Give me your Copy Card.

1300
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,400
Alright then.

1301
00:40:10,400 --> 00:40:12,200
The motive for murder between you two

1302
00:40:12,200 --> 00:40:12,920
