1303
00:40:13,560 --> 00:40:15,080
My son can actually prove

1304
00:40:15,080 --> 00:40:15,680
that he's innocent.

1305
00:40:15,680 --> 00:40:16,080
Why?

1306
00:40:16,080 --> 00:40:16,960
(How so?)

1307
00:40:16,960 --> 00:40:18,280
Because he already destroyed this.

1308
00:40:18,280 --> 00:40:20,720
There was no need for him
to kill An Er anymore.

1309
00:40:21,320 --> 00:40:23,040
The stuff had already been sent
to the hospital.

1310
00:40:23,040 --> 00:40:24,360
At most, it's just
getting a report done.

1311
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:25,640
Yeah.

1312
00:40:25,640 --> 00:40:27,640
Come on, we're in a new era!

1313
00:40:27,640 --> 00:40:28,180
(It's 2016!)

1314
00:40:28,240 --> 00:40:28,800
Although you said

1315
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:30,560
you didn't let An Er get this letter,

1316
00:40:30,560 --> 00:40:31,320
so he didn't know

1317
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:33,360
you weren't An Yi's biological son,

1318
00:40:33,360 --> 00:40:35,920
you already knew An Er
was investigating.

1319
00:40:36,200 --> 00:40:38,320
Your motive is completely valid.

1320
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:39,720
Ding, I can't help you anymore.

1321
00:40:39,720 --> 00:40:40,640
Just confess.

1322
00:40:42,620 --> 00:40:43,470
(Clues about Aunty Pai's
Cleaning Cart Scene)

1323
00:40:43,470 --> 00:40:44,240
(An Xiaoding and Aunty Pai
used each other)

1324
00:40:44,240 --> 00:40:45,720
(Motive for murder: Prevent An Er
from revealing his identity)

1325
00:40:45,720 --> 00:40:46,820
(An Xiaoding and An Yi
are not father and son)

1326
00:40:46,840 --> 00:40:48,560
Let's look at this black clip.

1327
00:40:48,560 --> 00:40:51,160
Quickly clear me of suspicion.

1328
00:40:51,640 --> 00:40:52,240
Your suspicion

1329
00:40:52,240 --> 00:40:53,840
can't be cleared anymore.

1330
00:40:53,900 --> 00:40:55,000
(Feeling wronged)

1331
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:55,440
Come.

1332
00:40:59,920 --> 00:41:00,760
A tablet!

1333
00:41:02,120 --> 00:41:03,360
It's a tablet!

1334
00:41:03,640 --> 00:41:04,800
"My ideal type"

1335
00:41:04,800 --> 00:41:05,960
Full spelling?

1336
00:41:05,960 --> 00:41:06,860
(The tablet needs a password to unlock)

1337
00:41:06,980 --> 00:41:07,800
(My ideal type)

1338
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:09,160
An Xiaoding.

1339
00:41:09,640 --> 00:41:10,640
Is this mine?

1340
00:41:11,080 --> 00:41:13,080
Yes. This belongs to Aunty Pai.

1341
00:41:13,360 --> 00:41:14,280
Then it should be An Xiaoding.

1342
00:41:14,280 --> 00:41:15,120
Have a try.

1343
00:41:15,120 --> 00:41:15,520
An

1344
00:41:15,520 --> 00:41:16,440
(First attempt: anxiaoding)

1345
00:41:16,440 --> 00:41:17,040
Xiao

1346
00:41:17,560 --> 00:41:17,800
Ding.

1347
00:41:19,360 --> 00:41:19,800
Wrong.

1348
00:41:23,000 --> 00:41:23,400
She...

1349
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:23,960
Not you?

1350
00:41:23,960 --> 00:41:24,960
(Not you?)

1351
00:41:24,960 --> 00:41:26,760
Her ideal type isn't An Xiaoding?

1352
00:41:27,840 --> 00:41:28,920
Bring over that cleaning bag.

1353
00:41:28,920 --> 00:41:29,960
My treasure.

1354
00:41:29,960 --> 00:41:30,640
Treasure?

1355
00:41:30,640 --> 00:41:31,800
(Missed clue recovered)
Let's see what's inside.

1356
00:41:31,800 --> 00:41:32,320
My treasure.

1357
00:41:32,320 --> 00:41:32,960
My treasure...

1358
00:41:34,680 --> 00:41:35,360
Who is this?

1359
00:41:37,300 --> 00:41:38,300
(Glass necklace)

1360
00:41:38,560 --> 00:41:39,320
While working,

1361
00:41:39,320 --> 00:41:40,960
her neck and hands were bare.

1362
00:41:40,960 --> 00:41:41,880
They won't be bare anymore soon.

1363
00:41:42,680 --> 00:41:43,560
Wasn't this necklace from you?

1364
00:41:43,560 --> 00:41:44,560
She said her neck was bare,

1365
00:41:44,560 --> 00:41:45,480
and you said it wouldn't be for long.

1366
00:41:45,480 --> 00:41:46,680
I didn't give it to her.

1367
00:41:46,680 --> 00:41:47,600
You didn't?

1368
00:41:48,480 --> 00:41:49,400
I didn't give it to her.

1369
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:52,800
If you didn't, then who did?

1370
00:41:54,080 --> 00:41:54,520
Pai...

1371
00:41:54,880 --> 00:41:55,400
Let me see.

1372
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:56,640
A huge piece...

1373
00:41:56,640 --> 00:41:57,080
Glass.

1374
00:41:58,040 --> 00:41:59,560
Who would know

1375
00:41:59,560 --> 00:42:00,760
