1376
00:42:00,760 --> 00:42:01,200
No, wait.

1377
00:42:01,200 --> 00:42:03,000
Our family makes glasses,

1378
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:05,080
and you're in charge
of the production line.

1379
00:42:05,080 --> 00:42:05,680
Yeah.

1380
00:42:05,680 --> 00:42:07,160
I'm in charge of the technical work.

1381
00:42:07,160 --> 00:42:08,240
Yeah.

1382
00:42:08,240 --> 00:42:09,520
Then that means...

1383
00:42:10,360 --> 00:42:11,040
He.

1384
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:12,920
Me?

1385
00:42:12,920 --> 00:42:13,600
What?

1386
00:42:14,040 --> 00:42:15,400
How dare he!

1387
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:16,640
That's very possible.

1388
00:42:17,280 --> 00:42:18,480
You brat,

1389
00:42:18,480 --> 00:42:20,800
you're holding the necklace so naturally.

1390
00:42:20,800 --> 00:42:22,560
I think you picked it out.

1391
00:42:23,520 --> 00:42:26,720
Because he's also one of the men
fighting for the inheritance.

1392
00:42:27,600 --> 00:42:28,800
Exactly.

1393
00:42:29,720 --> 00:42:31,560
You failed to see the true face
of your partner.

1394
00:42:32,720 --> 00:42:34,680
I failed to see the true face
of my partner!

1395
00:42:34,680 --> 00:42:35,320
Impossible.

1396
00:42:35,320 --> 00:42:36,360
It can't be him.

1397
00:42:36,360 --> 00:42:37,560
He's innocent and kind.

1398
00:42:37,620 --> 00:42:39,020
(Love has taken over her brain)

1399
00:42:39,640 --> 00:42:40,920
Don't worry, darling.

1400
00:42:40,920 --> 00:42:42,000
I can explain everything.

1401
00:42:44,240 --> 00:42:45,120
I believe you.

1402
00:42:46,920 --> 00:42:48,400
You brat.

1403
00:42:48,400 --> 00:42:49,200
You...

1404
00:42:50,120 --> 00:42:52,360
You were the harshest one.

1405
00:42:52,360 --> 00:42:54,000
How could you frame me?

1406
00:42:54,640 --> 00:42:55,640
Well...

1407
00:42:56,060 --> 00:42:58,260
(I don't like He anymore)

1408
00:42:58,520 --> 00:43:00,320
He was desperately trying
to pin the suspicion

1409
00:43:00,320 --> 00:43:01,200
(Saw it clearly)
on you.

1410
00:43:01,200 --> 00:43:02,040
He had his reasons too.

1411
00:43:02,820 --> 00:43:04,500
(Ding, don't cry)

1412
00:43:05,920 --> 00:43:08,080
Even if I gave her this,

1413
00:43:08,080 --> 00:43:09,120
even if there's

1414
00:43:09,920 --> 00:43:10,640
a secret...

1415
00:43:10,640 --> 00:43:12,120
Even if I had a secret with Aunty Pai,

1416
00:43:13,320 --> 00:43:14,880
what makes you say I killed An Er?

1417
00:43:14,880 --> 00:43:16,120
What does that have to do with him?

1418
00:43:19,240 --> 00:43:19,680
Wen,

1419
00:43:20,720 --> 00:43:21,960
