1420
00:43:21,960 --> 00:43:24,240
You and I aren't related by blood at all.

1421
00:43:25,080 --> 00:43:26,200
Yeah. We don't even
share the same dad anymore.

1422
00:43:26,260 --> 00:43:27,360
(Poor little thing)

1423
00:43:27,360 --> 00:43:28,160
Open it.

1424
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:30,120
He.

1425
00:43:30,120 --> 00:43:30,840
Ji.

1426
00:43:30,840 --> 00:43:32,800
Jia.

1427
00:43:33,080 --> 00:43:33,480
Hu.

1428
00:43:33,480 --> 00:43:36,240
Huan.

1429
00:43:36,240 --> 00:43:36,880
Okay.

1430
00:43:37,520 --> 00:43:38,080
Unlocked.

1431
00:43:38,080 --> 00:43:39,300
(Hubby King He)

1432
00:43:42,500 --> 00:43:43,260
(So shocked)

1433
00:43:44,360 --> 00:43:45,960
