You...

1434
00:43:45,960 --> 00:43:48,440
You jerk!

1435
00:43:49,000 --> 00:43:50,680
He Jiahuan.

1436
00:43:50,680 --> 00:43:51,360
There are several things.

1437
00:43:51,360 --> 00:43:52,000
