1439
00:43:53,600 --> 00:43:56,200
Hubby King He?

1440
00:43:58,540 --> 00:44:00,740
(Hubby King He)

1441
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:01,560
Hmm?

1442
00:44:01,560 --> 00:44:01,920
What?

1443
00:44:06,000 --> 00:44:06,760
Hubby?

1444
00:44:06,760 --> 00:44:07,840
Don't look.

1445
00:44:07,840 --> 00:44:08,440
Sit down.

1446
00:44:08,760 --> 00:44:09,320
Wait a second.

1447
