Hubby King He?

1452
00:44:17,670 --> 00:44:19,520
I believe you.

1453
00:44:20,080 --> 00:44:20,440
Hey!

1454
00:44:20,440 --> 00:44:21,200
Ning!

1455
00:44:21,200 --> 00:44:22,000
