1456
00:44:24,480 --> 00:44:25,800
Geez!

1457
00:44:26,160 --> 00:44:27,360
Jerk!

1458
00:44:27,840 --> 00:44:29,400
I think you should explain

1459
00:44:29,400 --> 00:44:31,240
