1466
00:44:39,320 --> 00:44:40,600
(The top husband, Hubby King)

1467
00:44:40,600 --> 00:44:41,520
Alright.

1468
00:44:42,360 --> 00:44:44,680
The timeline moves forward

1469
00:44:44,680 --> 00:44:46,320
