1491
00:45:36,480 --> 00:45:36,960
She said,

1492
00:45:36,960 --> 00:45:37,600
"Sir,

1493
00:45:38,000 --> 00:45:38,840
I'm sorry.

1494
00:45:38,840 --> 00:45:39,760
