You fired a hard shot
straight into my heart.

1500
00:45:51,120 --> 00:45:53,080
"How's the matter with Uncle Er going?"

1501
00:45:53,080 --> 00:45:53,880
"Still investigating."

1502
00:45:53,880 --> 00:45:55,600
"There's been new progress."

1503
00:45:55,960 --> 00:45:56,280
