1659
00:50:56,200 --> 00:50:56,760
Right.

1660
00:50:56,960 --> 00:50:57,400
It's He's...

1661
00:50:57,400 --> 00:50:57,680
Let's search first.

1662
00:50:57,680 --> 00:50:58,160
He, come here.

1663
00:50:58,960 --> 00:51:00,440
