1664
00:51:00,440 --> 00:51:00,760
Yes.

1665
00:51:03,440 --> 00:51:03,960
Lock screen.

1666
00:51:04,760 --> 00:51:05,200
Nice.

1667
00:51:05,300 --> 00:51:07,140
